quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  4,27,"God wants to turn to you, but those who follow the lusts want you to deviate, a great deviation"
  4,28,"God wants to reduce your (burdens), as the human being is created weak"
  4,29,"You who believe, do not falsely eat up one another's properties among yourselves, but let there be trade among you with your mutual satisfaction. And do not kill yourselves (each other). God is merciful to you"
  4,30,"Anyone who does this due to aggression and wrongdoing, We are going to enter (and burn) him in a fire, and that is easy for God"
  4,31,"If you avoid the big ones that you are prohibited from it, We remove your sins from you and admit you into a noble place"
  4,32,"And do not wish for what God graced some of you over others with it. Men have a share of what they did, and women have a share of what they did. And ask God from His grace. God knows everything"
  4,33,"For everyone We appointed inheritors for what the parents and the relatives left behind, and those you contracted by your oath, so give them their share. God is indeed witness over everything"